parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk or lurch, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents or loss of power.
symptoms: The transmission shifts hard
hesitates

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Loss of Power and Engine Stalling

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electronic Shifter and Transmission Module Issues

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine and head gasket issues can cause the engine to fail, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failures of the Uconnect infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also render safety features such as rear warning systems and navigation systems unusable.

the radio changes stations randomly

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failures of the electrical system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the vehicle may stall or lose power while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust on the hood and body of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the rust may weaken the structural integrity of the vehicle.
